/8/4/d/c/thumb_252934012.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos2.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/3/8/b/2/thumb_244454514.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos4.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/a/7/4/5/thumb_250902821.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos2.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/3/f/9/0/thumb_243796272.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos4.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/7/5/5/1/thumb_246750033.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos1.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/7/8/e/4/thumb_249810948.jpeg" /></div>\n</p></div>\n<p style="line-height:16px">Welkom op WordPress Meetup Nijmegen, georganiseerd door Savvii &#038; Yoast.Het wordt een mooie avond met wederom enkele topsprekers en natuurlijk met jullie.Programma   19.30u Zaal open   19.45u Welkomstwoord  20.00u Keynote &#8211; Theo van der Zee   20.45u Pauze   21.00u Special Track &#8211; nog niet aangekondigd     22.00u NaborrelenFocus van de meetup Deze&#8230;</p>\n</p></div>\n<p style="margin:10px 0 0;"><a href="http://www.meetup.com/WordPress-Meetup-Nijmegen/events/227854428/" target="_blank" class="mu_button"><strong>Check out this Meetup &rarr;</strong></a></p>\n</div>\n<hr />\n<h3>WordPress Meetup 010 &#8211; 14 September 2015</h3>\n<style type="text/css">#meetup_oembed .mu_clearfix:after { visibility: hidden; display: block; font-size: 0; content: " "; clear: both; height: 0; }* html #meetup_oembed .mu_clearfix, *:first-child+html #meetup_oembed .mu_clearfix { zoom: 1; }#meetup_oembed { background:#eee;border:1px solid #ccc;padding:10px;-moz-border-radius:3px;-webkit-border-radius:3px;border-radius:3px;margin:0; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; }#meetup_oembed h3 { font-weight:normal; margin:0 0 10px; padding:0; line-height:26px; font-family:Georgia,Palatino,serif; font-size:24px }#meetup_oembed p { margin: 0 0 10px; padding:0; line