"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos2.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/6/5/f/2/thumb_246866098.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos1.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/4/3/9/0/thumb_243557296.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos1.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/6/a/c/thumb_249181708.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos1.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/a/d/d/4/thumb_245804500.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos1.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/9/1/1/d/thumb_247537149.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos4.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/3/4/d/b/thumb_244033531.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos3.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/9/2/0/a/thumb_248617386.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos2.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/8/0/0/b/thumb_246632779.jpeg" /></div>\n</p></div>\n<p style="line-height:16px">Servus! Houden we het een beetje uit met de warmte? Aankomende WPMeetup010 zal weer interessant worden. We kunnen deze keer twee diverse talks verwachten. 1 technische en 1 business talk:Programma19:00 Inloop &#8211; drankje aangeboden door het #WPMeetup010 team19:30 &#8220;Een blik achter de schermen bij nrc.nl&#8221; door Appie Verschoor20:15 Pauze*20:30 &#8220;Bui&#8230;</p>\n</p></div>\n<p style="margin:10px 0 0;"><a href="http://www.meetup.com/Rotterdam-WordPress-Meetup/events/224473700/" target="_blank" class="mu_button"><strong>Check out this Meetup &rarr;</strong></a></p>\n</div>\n<hr />\n<h3>WordPress Meetup Utrecht woensdag 16 september 2015</h3>\n<style type="text/css">#meetup_oembed .mu_clearfix:after { visibility: hidden; display: block; font-size: 0; content: " "; clear: both; height: 0; }* html #meetup_oembed .mu_clearfix, *:first-child+html #meetup_oembed .mu_clearfix { zoom: 1; }#meetup_oembed { background:#eee;border:1px solid #ccc;padding:10px;-moz-border-radius:3px;-webkit-bor