otos/member/a/f/a/e/thumb_246644974.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos1.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/3/9/8/f/thumb_246794735.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos2.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/e/7/8/0/thumb_242099264.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos3.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/2/7/0/thumb_242100624.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos3.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/4/b/7/a/thumb_235039322.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos4.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/a/6/5/6/thumb_96222582.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos4.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/c/8/f/c/thumb_143931452.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos1.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/c/4/7/e/thumb_230750302.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos3.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/4/5/b/e/thumb_250757854.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos1.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/3/9/7/5/thumb_241934709.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos3.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/3/d/4/8/thumb_241515688.jpeg" /></div>\n</p></div>\n<p style="line-height:16px">Op woensdag 16 september zal opnieuw een Utrechtse WordPress MeetUp plaatsvinden. Deze WordPress meetup is voor iedereen die graag met WordPress werkt, of het nu professioneel of als hobby is. Per MeetUp vinden er 2 presentaties plaats. En na de talks is er nog tijd voor een praatje met een drankje. Entree is gratis. Ruimtesponsor is net als vorige&#8230;</p>\n</p></div>\n<p style="margin:10px 0 0;"><a href="http://www.meetup.com/WordPress-Meetup-Utrecht/events/224165277/" target="_blank" class="mu_button"><strong>Check out this Meetup &rarr;</strong></a></p>\n</div>\n<hr />\n<h3>WordPress Meetup Enschede 22 september 2015</h3>\n<style type="text/css">#meetup_oembed .mu_clearfix:after { visibility: hidden; display: block; font-size: 0; content: " "; clear: both; height: 0; }* html #meetup_oembed .mu_clearfix, *:first-child+html #meetup_oembed .mu_clearfix { zoom: 1; }#meetup_oembed { background:#eee;border:1px solid #ccc;padding:10px;-moz-border-radius:3px;-webkit-border-radius:3px;border-radius:3px;margin:0; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; }#meetup_oembed h3 { font-weight:normal; margin:0 0 10px; padding:0; line-height:26px; font-family:Georgia,Palatino,serif; font-size:24px }#meetup_oembed p { margin: 0 0 10px; padding:0; line-height:16px; }#meetup_oembed img { border:none; margin:0; padding:0; }#meetup_oembed a, #meetup_oembed a:visited, #meetup_oembed a:link { color: #1B76B3; text-decoration: none; cursor: hand; cursor: pointer; }#meetup_oembed a:hover { color: #1B76B3; text-decoration: underline; }#meetup_oembed a.mu_button { font-size:14px; -moz-border-radius:3px;-webkit-border-radius:3px;border-radius:3px;border:2px solid #A7241D;color:white!important;text-decoration:none;background-color: #CA3E47; background-image: -moz-linear-gradient(top, #ca3e47, #a8252e); background-image: -webkit-gradient(linear, left bottom, left top, color-stop(0, #a8252e), color-stop(1, #ca3e47));disvplay:inline-block;padding:5px 10px; }#meetup_oembed a.mu_button:hover { color: #fff!important; text-decoration: none; }#meetup_oembed .photo { width:50px; height:50px; overflow:hidden;background:#ccc;float:left;margin:0 5px 0 0;text-align:center;padding:1px; }#meetup_oembed .photo img { height:50px }#meetup_oembed .number { font-size:18px; }#meetup_oembed .thing { text-transform: uppercase; color: #555; }</style>\n<div id="meetup_oembed" style="height:302px">\n<div style="max-height:262px;overflow:hidden">\n<h3>WordPress Meetup Enschede 22 september 2015</h3>\n<p style="margin:5px 0;font-size:16px">Tuesday, Sep 22, 2015,  7:00 PM</p>\n<p style="margin: 0 0 5px;"><span style="font-size:14px">TriMM</span><br /><span style="font-size:12px;">Moutlaan 25, 7523 MC Enschede, NL</span></p>\n<p>          <span style="color:#4F8A10;font-size:16px;">38 Members Went</span>\n<div style="margin:5px 0 10px" class="mu_clearfix">\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos1.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/7/f/a/0/thumb_114512672.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos3.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/5/1/f/0/thumb_246320976.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos3.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/2/c/e/e/thumb_248111502.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos3.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/4/9/3/c/thumb_244038748.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos2.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/6/0/f/4/thumb_243504820.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos3.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/c/b/9/a/thumb_78952122.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos4.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/8/c/a/b/thumb_249696011.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos3.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/b/b/3/f/thumb_249947935.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos3.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/c/2/c/d/thumb_241429869.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos3.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/6/c/b/0/thumb_247887824.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos3.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/8/4/e/b/thumb_243934027.jpeg" /></div>\n</p></div>\n<p style="line-height:16px">De volgende meetup staat gepland voor dinsdag 22 september.Hou deze meetup in de gaten, hier maken we binnenkort meer details bekend over sprekers en onderwerpen.19:00: Inloop  19:20: Opening  19:30: Marko Heijnen &#8211; Mijn site beveiliging 20:15: Floris P Lof &#8211; Den rattenvanger van WordPress 21:00: Q&#038;A sessie  21:30: Borrel  22:30: AfsluitingMarko&#8230;</p>\n</p></div>\n<p style="margin:10px 0 0;"><a href="http://www.meetup.com/WordPress-Meetup-Enschede/events/223462076/" target="_blank" class="mu_button"><strong>Check out this Meetup &rarr;</strong></a></p>\n</div>\n<hr />\n<h3><del>Eerste</del> De derde WordPress Meetup in 033</h3>\n<style type="text/css">#meetup_oembed .mu_clearfix:after { visibility: hidden; display: block; font-size: 0; content: " "; clear: both; height: 0; }* html #meetup_oembed .mu_clearfix, *:first-child+html #meetup_oembed .mu_clearfix { zoom: 1; }#meetup_oembed { background:#eee;border:1px solid #ccc;padding:10px;-moz-border-radius:3px;-webkit-border-radius:3px;border-radius:3px;margin:0; font-family: ''Helvetica Neue'', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; }#meetup_oembed h3 { font-weight:normal; margin:0 0 10px; padding:0; line-height:26px; font-family:Georgia,Palatino,serif; font-size:24px }#meetup_oembed p { margin: 0 0 10px; padding:0; line-height:16px; }#meetup_oembed img { border:none; margin:0; padding:0; }#meetup_oembed a, #meetup_oembed a:visited, #meetup_oembed a:link { color: #1B76B3; text-decoration: none; cursor: hand; cursor: pointer; }#meetup_oembed a:hover { color: #1B76B3; text-decoration: underline; }#meetup_oembed a.mu_button { font-size:14px; -moz-border-radius:3px;-webkit-border-radius:3px;border-radius:3px;border:2px solid #A7241D;color:white!important;text-decoration:none;background-color: #CA3E47; background-image: -moz-linear-gradient(top, #ca3e47, #a8252e); background-image: -webkit-gradient(linear, left bottom, left top, color-stop(0, #a8252e), color-stop(1, #ca3e47));disvplay:inline-block;padding:5px 10px; }#meetup_oembed a.mu_button:hover { color: #fff!important; text-decoration: none; }#meetup_oembed .photo { width:50px; height:50px; overflow:hidden;background:#ccc;float:left;margin:0 5px 0 0;text-align:center;padding:1px; }#meetup_oembed .photo img { height:50px }#meetup_oembed .number { font-size:18px; }#meetup_oembed .thing { text-transform: uppercase; color: #555; }</style>\n<div id="meetup_oembed" style="height:302px">\n<div style="max-height:262px;overflow:hidden">\n<h3>WPM033 2015</h3>\n<p style="margin:5px 0;font-size:16px">Thursday, Oct 29, 2015,  7:00 PM</p>\n<p style="margin: 0 0 5px;"><span style="font-size:14px">Enrise</span><br /><span style="font-size:12px;">Grote Koppel 7 Amersfoort, NL</span></p>\n<p>          <span style="color:#4F8A10;font-size:16px;">26 Developers Went</span>\n<div style="margin:5px 0 10px" class="mu_clearfix">\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos1.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/7/8/5/e/thumb_247770814.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos1.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/7/8/7/a/thumb_231510842.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos3.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/5/6/3/4/thumb_242122068.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos1.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/8/6/3/4/thumb_242914356.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos2.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/7/6/b/7/thumb_250530391.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos2.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/6/a/5/8/thumb_249207224.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos2.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/7/b/a/4/thumb_234871652.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos3.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/4/d/3/9/thumb_246979769.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos4.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/a/a/e/6/thumb_250963750.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos4.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/2/8/8/2/thumb_242710370.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i0.wp.com/photos3.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/7/8/2/0/thumb_119850752.jpeg" /></div>\n</p></div>\n<p style="line-height:16px">De WordPress Meetup in Amersfoort zal 29 oktober gehouden worden in het pand van Enrise. Enrise zit nabij de oude haven van Amersfoort en is goed bereikbaar met zowel de auto als het openbaar vervoer. Er is plek voor 30 bezoekers.   Inloop vanaf 18:30 en start van de eerste talk om 19:00.   Talk 1: David de Boer  David is internet­ondernemer sinds &#8230;</p>\n</p></div>\n<p style="margin:10px 0 0;"><a href="http://www.meetup.com/WordPress-033/events/223937621/" target="_blank" class="mu_button"><strong>Check out this Meetup &rarr;</strong></a></p>\n</div>\n<hr />\n<p>Zoals je ziet is er voldoende te beleven om je WordPress kennis aan te vullen en vakbroeders te ontmoeten!</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:85:"https://nl.wordpress.org/2015/08/07/deze-wordpress-meetups-staan-in-de-planning/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"2";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:42:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:25:"WordCamp Netherlands 2015";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:62:"https://nl.wordpress.org/2015/07/08/wordcamp-netherlands-2015/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:70:"https://nl.wordpress.org/2015/07/08/wordcamp-netherlands-2015/#respond";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Wed, 08 Jul 2015 11:34:01 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:8:"WordCamp";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"https://nl.wordpress.org/?p=353";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:356:"WordCamp Netherlands 2015 komt eraan. De voorbereidingen zijn inmiddels gestart en we kunnen al wat feitjes verklappen. 5e editie Dit jaar is de 5e WordCamp Netherlands. Na 2009, 2010, 2011, 2012 en 2014 (2013 was WordCamp Europe in Leiden) is dit de vijfde WordCamp Netherlands. Een mijlpaal, en dat vieren we graag met alle aanwezigen. Locatie [&#8230;]";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:15:"Remkus de Vries";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1750:"<p>WordCamp Netherlands 2015 komt eraan. De voorbereidingen zijn inmiddels gestart en we kunnen al wat feitjes verklappen.</p>\n<h2>5e editie</h2>\n<p>Dit jaar is de 5e WordCamp Netherlands. Na 2009, 2010, 2011, 2012 en 2014 (2013 was WordCamp Europe in Leiden) is dit de vijfde WordCamp Netherlands. Een mijlpaal, en dat vieren we graag met alle aanwezigen.</p>\n<h2>Locatie</h2>\n<p>De locatie voor WordCamp Nederland 2015 zal wederom <a title="Locatie" href="https://netherlands.wordcamp.org/2014/locatie/">Seats2Meet</a> in Utrecht zijn. Voor ervaren bezoekers is dit geen verrassing. Alle voorgaande edities van <a href="https://twitter.com/search?q=%23WCNL&amp;src=typd" target="_blank">#WCNL</a> vonden plaats bij Seats2Meet.</p>\n<h2>Kaartverkoop</h2>\n<p>Binnenkort gaat de kaartverkoop starten. Hou de site in de gaten of abonneer je op updates en krijg automatisch bericht van nieuws.</p>\n<h2>Sprekers</h2>\n<p>Ook voor deze editie van WordCamp Netherlands zoeken we weer sprekers. We publiceren morgen onze <em>Call For Speakers</em> waarin je jezelf aan kunt melden om te komen spreken. Morgen volgt hier meer informatie over!</p>\n<h2>Sponsors</h2>\n<p>We zoeken een aantal sponsoren die ons helpen om hiervan de beste WordCamp tot nu toe te maken. Mede dankzij jouw bijdrage wordt WordCamp Nederland 2015 de beste Nederlandse WordCamp ooit.  Binnenkort zal de sponsor informatie op de site gezet worden.</p>\n<h2>Vrijwilligers</h2>\n<p>WordCamp Nederland zou niet bestaan zonder vrijwilligers. Op dit moment bestaat de organisatie uit vijf mensen. Dat is lang niet genoeg om te zorgen dat alles vlekkeloos verloopt.</p>\n<p>Voor meer informatie kijk op de site voor <a href="https://netherlands.wordcamp.org/2015">WordCamp NL 2015</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:67:"https://nl.wordpress.org/2015/07/08/wordcamp-netherlands-2015/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:42:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:13:"WordPress 4.2";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:50:"https://nl.wordpress.org/2015/04/23/wordpress-4-2/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:58:"https://nl.wordpress.org/2015/04/23/wordpress-4-2/#respond";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Thu, 23 Apr 2015 11:14:33 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:7:"Release";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"https://nl.wordpress.org/?p=347";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:389:"Vandaag is WordPress versie 4.2  vrijgegeven met de volgende features en verbeteringen: Een eenvoudigere manier om inhoud te delen Selecteren, bewerken en publiceren. Wordt bekend met de verbeterde &#8216;Press this&#8217; optie. Via het Extra menu kan je de &#8216;Press this&#8217; toevoegen aan je bookmarks of koppelen op je home-scherm van je mobiel apparaat. Zodra dit is [&#8230;]";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:15:"Remkus de Vries";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:3974:"<p>Vandaag is WordPress versie 4.2  vrijgegeven met de volgende features en verbeteringen:</p>\n<h3>Een eenvoudigere manier om inhoud te delen</h3>\n<p>Selecteren, bewerken en publiceren. Wordt bekend met de verbeterde &#8216;Press this&#8217; optie. Via het <a href="http://zandbox.dev/wp-admin/tools.php">Extra</a> menu kan je de &#8216;Press this&#8217; toevoegen aan je bookmarks of koppelen op je home-scherm van je mobiel apparaat. Zodra dit is geïnstalleerd kan je nieuwe berichten delen met de snelheid van het licht. Het delen van favoriete video&#8217;s, afbeeldingen en tekst is nog nooit zo eenvoudig geweest.</p>\n<p><img class="aligncenter" src="https://s.w.org/images/core/4.2/press-this.jpg" alt="" width="1050" height="874" /></p>\n<h3>Uitgebreide karakterset ondersteuning</h3>\n<p>Het schrijven in WordPress, onafhankelijke van je taal, is beter geworden. WordPress 4.2. biedt ondersteuning voor nieuwe karaktersets zoals Chinese, Japanse en Koreaanse karakters. Daarnaast ook muzikale, wiskundige symbolen en hiërogliefen.</p>\n<p>Maak je geen gebruik van deze karakters? Je kan nog steeds je lol op — emoji&#8217;s zijn nu beschikbaar in WordPress. Gebruik je creativiteit en verrijk je bericht met <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/72x72/1f499.png" alt="💙" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />, <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/72x72/1f438.png" alt="🐸" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />, <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/72x72/1f412.png" alt="🐒" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />, <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/72x72/1f355.png" alt="🍕" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> en vele andere <a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Emoji">emoji&#8217;s</a>.</p>\n<p><img class="aligncenter" src="https://s.w.org/images/core/4.2/unicode.png" alt="" width="1000" height="832" /></p>\n<h4>Thema&#8217;s wisselen met de Thema Customizer</h4>\n<p><img class="aligncenter" src="https://s.w.org/images/core/4.2/theme-switcher.png" alt="" /></p>\n<p>Door de geïnstalleerde thema&#8217;s bladeren en previewen met de Thema Customizer. Zorg ervoor dat het thema er fantastisch uitziet met<em>jouw</em> content voordat deze wordt geactiveerd op de site.</p>\n<h4>En nog meer embeds</h4>\n<p><img class="aligncenter" src="https://s.w.org/images/core/4.2/embeds.png" alt="" /><br />\nLinks plakken vanuit Tumblr.com en Kickstarter en bekijk hoe de magie van de editor zijn werk doet. Met elke release zal het publiceren en bewerken steeds dichter bij elkaar komen.</p>\n<h4>Gestroomlijnde plugin updates</h4>\n<p><img class="aligncenter" src="https://s.w.org/images/core/4.2/plugins.png" alt="" /></p>\n<p>Vaarwel met het saaie laadscherm, hallo strakke en eenvoudige plugin updates. Klik op <em>Nu bijwerken</em> en zie wat de magie zal doen.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>Andere verbeteringen:</h3>\n<div class="feature-section col two-col">\n<div>\n<h4>utf8mb4 ondersteuning</h4>\n<p>Database karakter encoding is aangepast van utf8 naar utf8mb4. Hierdoor is er ondersteuning voor de nieuwe 4-byte karakters.</p>\n<h4>JavaScript toegankelijkheid</h4>\n<p>Het is nu mogelijk hoorbare meldingen naar schermlezers te sturen in JavaScript met <code>wp.a11y.speak()</code>. Geeft het door via een string en een update wordt verstuurd naar een dedicated ARIA live meldingengebied.</p>\n</div>\n<div class="last-feature">\n<h4>Splitsen van gedeelde termen</h4>\n<p>Termen die zijn gedeeld tussen meerder taxonomieën worden gesplitst zodra één van hen wordt bijgewerkt. Je kan hier meer over lezen in het<a href="https://developer.wordpress.org/plugins/taxonomy/working-with-split-terms-in-wp-4-2/">Plugin-ontwikkelaar handboek</a>.</p>\n<h4>Complexe query sortering</h4>\n<p><code>WP_Query</code>, <code>WP_Comment_Query</code>, en <code>WP_User_Query</code> ondersteunen nu complexe sortering met gelabelde meta query clausules.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:55:"https://nl.wordpress.org/2015/04/23/wordpress-4-2/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rs