(65, 1, '2017-02-20 08:39:54', '2017-02-20 08:39:54', 'Op 10 maart ruilt deze man <a href="https://www.facebook.com/jhdinolovendegem/" data-hovercard="/ajax/hovercard/page.php?id=286688938033341&amp;extragetparams=%7B%22directed_target_id%22%3A741748466007061%7D" data-hovercard-prefer-more-content-show="1">JH Dino</a> en Arabeatz in voor onze tweede editie van Shellshock in De Voute. Of misschien kent u hem nog van Drum ''n Bassics of Jackhammer festival? Zo niet: ga dat zien!', '✖✖ ARABIT ✖✖', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '%e2%9c%96%e2%9c%96-arabit-%e2%9c%96%e2%9c%96', '', '', '2017-02-20 08:39:54', '2017-02-20 08:39:54', '', 0, 'http://localhost/cmp2/popup/?p=65', 0, 'post', '', 0),
